# Changelog

## 0.9.x (under development)

*   The internal `Cdeadwood` function gained a new argument: `connected`.
    Allows choosing between chopping trees into chunks (false, the default)
    and branch trimming (true).


## 0.9.0 (2026-02-13)

*   [Python] Initial PyPI release.

*   [R] Initial CRAN release.
